Todo app

parts to it:
1. login page
- user must be able to register
- user must receive an email confirming her/her registration
- user must be able to reset their password vie email
- user should be able to logout

2. todo list
- user can add, delet and edit entry
-- the editing part must include changing of date
- when adding entry it should add a timestamp
- also when adding user is asked for defining a due date
- until one day before due date entry should be green
- on due date entry should change to yellow
- when due date is reached it should change background color to red


3. user profile
- user should be able to set a profile picture
- user should be able to deregister



